OL,3,CAsylum hotel arsonist given joint
OL,4,Clongest riots sentence
OL,6,FLevi Fishlock was a prominent figure
OL,7,Fin the rioting outside the Holiday Inn
OL,8,FExpress at Manvers, Rotherham, with a
OL,9,Fjudge saying he "played a part in
OL,10,Falmost every aspect of the racist mob
OL,11,Fviolence on that terrible day in
OL,12,FAugust".
OL,14,FFishlock, of Sheffield Road, Barnsley,
OL,15,Fpleaded guilty at Sheffield Crown
OL,16,FCourt to violent disorder and arson
OL,17,Fwith intent to endanger life.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/12
