OL,3,CAsylum hotel arsonist given joint
OL,4,Clongest riots sentence
OL,6,FRecorder of Sheffield Judge Jeremy
OL,7,FRichardson KC said the case was one of
OL,8,Fthe most serious he had dealt with as
OL,9,Fhe jailed Fishlock for nine years,
OL,10,Fwith an extended five-year period on
OL,11,Flicence.
OL,13,FIt is the joint-highest sentence given
OL,14,Ffor the summer's riots, with Thomas
OL,15,FBirley, 27, of Swinton in South
OL,16,FYorkshire, also jailed for nine years
OL,17,Fin September.
