OL,3,CAsylum hotel arsonist given joint
OL,4,Clongest riots sentence
OL,6,FThe court heard the 31-year-old was
OL,7,F"very identifiable" by his distinctive
OL,8,Fpurple England football shirt with
OL,9,F"Bellingham" written on the back.
OL,11,FHe was part of a group shouting abuse
OL,12,Fand racial slurs, at one point tapping
OL,13,Fthe England badge on his shirt.
OL,15,FJudge Richardson said the defendant
OL,16,Fwas "involved in almost every arena of
OL,17,Fracist criminal conduct that day".
