OL,3,CAsylum hotel arsonist given joint
OL,4,Clongest riots sentence
OL,6,FAs the violence escalated Fishlock was
OL,7,Fseen adding planks of wood to a large
OL,8,Fburning wheelie bin that was pushed up
OL,9,Fagainst the hotel, "intending to
OL,10,Fendanger the lives of many people
OL,11,Ftrapped in the hotel", the judge said.
OL,13,FFishlock also helped build barricades
OL,14,Fthat were then set on fire and made
OL,15,Fthreatening gestures with a sharp
OL,16,Fobject towards people who were inside
OL,17,Fthe hotel looking out through the
OL,18,Fwindows.
