OL,3,CAsylum hotel arsonist given joint
OL,4,Clongest riots sentence
OL,6,FHe was also seen smashing the hotel
OL,7,Fwindows by throwing bricks and paving
OL,8,Fslabs at them, destroying fencing
OL,9,Faround the hotel and smashing up an
OL,10,Fair conditioning unit.
OL,12,FThe court heard later in the day he
OL,13,Fwas part of a group who attacked
OL,14,Fincoming police vehicles with rocks.
OL,16,FAt one point he threw a missile
OL,17,Ftowards a police officer's legs,
OL,18,Faiming for the area that was not
OL,19,Fprotected by a riot shield, it was
OL,20,Fsaid.
