OL,4,Clongest riots sentence
OL,6,FAfter he was arrested in the days
OL,7,Ffollowing the riot, Fishlock told
OL,8,Fofficers driving him to the station
OL,9,Fthat he knew why he had been arrested
OL,10,Fand that it was "for a good cause".
OL,12,FIn mitigation, the court heard
OL,13,FFishlock, who has a young daughter,
OL,14,Fhad protracted difficulties with
OL,15,Fanxiety and depression, and a
OL,16,F"problematic relationship" with drugs.
