OL,3,CAsylum hotel arsonist given joint
OL,4,Clongest riots sentence
OL,6,FThe defendant became the second person
OL,7,Fto be sentenced for arson with intent
OL,8,Fto endanger life following the 12
OL,9,Fhours of violence in Manvers on 4
OL,10,FAugust which left 64 police officers,
OL,11,Fthree horses and a dog injured.
OL,13,FIn September painter and decorator
OL,14,FThomas Birley, 27, was jailed for nine
OL,15,Fyears after pleading guilty to arson
OL,16,Fwith intent to endanger life, violent
OL,17,Fdisorder and possession of an
OL,18,Foffensive weapon for his actions that
OL,19,Fday.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/12
