OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F361A1734021621
OL,3,CAsylum hotel arsonist given joint
OL,4,Clongest riots sentence
OL,6,FMore than 70 men have so far been
OL,7,Fjailed for their roles in the disorder
OL,8,Foutside the hotel.
OL,10,FSheffield Crown Court has heard how
OL,11,Fmore than 200 asylum seekers were
OL,12,Ftrapped in the upper floors as rioters
OL,13,Fsmashed windows and set light to the
OL,14,Fbin, which was pushed against a fire
OL,15,Fdoor.
OL,17,FHotel staff have told the court how
OL,18,Fthey barricaded themselves into a
OL,19,Fpanic room during the rioting, fearing
OL,20,Fthey would die as they smelt the smoke.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/12
