OL,3,CAsylum hotel arsonist given joint
OL,4,Clongest riots sentence
OL,6,FJudge Richardson said: "It has been my
OL,7,Fmisfortune, as well as my duty, to
OL,8,Fhave sentenced most of the cases
OL,9,Farising from the public disorder in
OL,10,FRotherham.
OL,12,F"This is unquestionably one of the
OL,13,Fworst of the many cases which have
OL,14,Fcome before this court concerning the
OL,15,Fevents in Rotherham.
OL,17,F"You were involved in almost every
OL,18,Farena of racist criminal conduct that
OL,19,Fday.
OL,26,@nD@XOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
