OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F361A1734021621
OL,3,CAsylum hotel arsonist given joint
OL,4,Clongest riots sentence
OL,6,F"Your conduct, and the conduct of that
OL,7,Fmob, has cast a dark and ugly stain
OL,8,Facross the reputation of Rotherham and
OL,9,FSouth Yorkshire."
OL,11,FHe went on to say: "You did not start
OL,12,Fthe fire but you added to it and
OL,13,Fhelped fuel the flames. That is as
OL,14,Fserious as starting it."
OL,16,FChris Hartley, of the Crown
OL,17,FProsecution Service, said: "The tough
OL,18,Fsentence imposed today should serve as
OL,19,Fa lesson for anyone considering taking
OL,20,Fpart in this type of disorder in
OL,21,Ffuture.
