OL,3,CAsylum hotel arsonist given joint
OL,4,Clongest riots sentence
OL,6,F"Fishlock played a prominent part in
OL,7,Fthese shameful acts of senseless
OL,8,Fviolence, which terrified the
OL,9,Fresidents and staff of the hotel and
OL,10,Fcaused significant amounts of physical
OL,11,Fdamage.
OL,13,F"Highly experienced police officers
OL,14,Fdescribed the disorder as the worst
OL,15,Fthey had ever seen in their careers.
OL,16,FThe violence had left them in fear for
OL,17,Ftheir lives."
